variable.upper makes everything uppercase

variable.replace('Bob','Jane') ##makes a copy and then replaces Bob w/ Jane

variable.lstrip ##strips from the left all spaces
variable.rstrip ##strips from the right
variable.strip ##gets rid of all white space on left and right
variable.startswith('searchterm') ##returns true or false based on start letter

